txt.en: The mysterious old man sent you to Thrug-unur to defeat the captain of the Moria-goblins there.\n\nYou should defeat some of his minions, as well.
The mysterious old man sent you to Thrug-unur to defeat the captain of the Moria-goblins there.

Goblins can be found at Thrug-unur, north-east of Éomer's Vengeance in the Entwash Vale.\n\nYou should defeat as many goblins as you can to further aid the cause of Thane Béortnoth and the survivors of Thornhope.
